text: Eden Riegel (born January 1, 1981) is an American actress. She acts mostly in television programs. She played Bianca Montgomery in the ABC soap opera All My Children. She played Heather in The Young and the Restless. Riegel was born in Washington, D.C. ==References== Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Washington, D.C.
